OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening with perhaps the odd
OL,7,Fshower in the east and clear spells
OL,8,Felsewhere. Dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fspells, leading to a cold night and a
OL,10,Ffrost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FIt will be a largely dry day
OL,13,Fwith bright and sunny spells, the odd
OL,14,Fisolated shower possible. Turning
OL,15,Fcloudier in the evening with rain
OL,16,Fspreading eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
