OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain Sunday
OL,7,Fand Monday as winds strengthen, some
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter intervals possible,
OL,9,Fespecially east. Drier Tuesday with
OL,10,Fjust the odd shower and sunny spells.
